{"tid":520702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實而家嘅老人家係咪比社會遺棄咗？","createTime":"2018-01-05T16:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T18:29:12.000Z","uid":142212,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"871d2be15bf12ee001aa807df72e53d5344c280d","tid":520702,"uid":142212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"搭車 行路 個個都拎住部手機<br />\n但係老人家唔識用<br />\n以前搭巴士都話可以同人吹幾句水<br />\n但係而家個個係度篤手機<br />\n望住佢哋 會唔會覺得自己好似一個outsider咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   人哋睇到嘅嘢自己又睇唔到<br />\n唯有周圍望下風景 訓下覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後退休又好似冇咩做咁<br />\n試下想像下無嘢做又無手機玩嘅生活<br />\n仔女又嫁晒出去<br />\n諗起都覺得悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好廢老前廢老後<br />\n你哋試下想像下自己嘅嫲嫲爺爺<br />\n就會覺得心痛<br />\n自己越嚟越大 又冇以前咁多時間陪佢哋<br />\n真係要珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f01d61eb45e6adc5c588e88452df47b530a0939","tid":520702,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"我成日經過d公園都見到d阿婆成碌木咁坐係到"},{"pid":"1ca6ec04ce4aa14416be893dfe03f2c3012855da","tid":520702,"uid":142212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"25a4a6863461d869bca4d958daca8691386be2d4","tid":520702,"uid":142212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"cd056a09d1fa684abc1794e6d00575edcc3a93bf","tid":520702,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"通常唔識同仔女相處 到老無人理 唔出奇"},{"pid":"2cd52c7d2ae23ab89992df249fabde244c4aa28a","tid":520702,"uid":28831,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:12:32.000Z","msg":"所以話人係唔需要生存到咁耐<br />\n老左只會多病痛，同社會脫節，孤獨<br />\n咁不如係人生最輝煌既時候死反而仲好"},{"pid":"c923728a1ece8e807950f26176abdba7ea910573","tid":520702,"uid":17616,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20